.SH "NAME"
XML::Handler::CanonXMLWriter \- output XML in canonical XML format
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.Vb 1
\& use XML::Handler::CanonXMLWriter;
\&
\& $writer = XML::Handler::CanonXMLWriter OPTIONS;
\& $parser\->parse(Handler => $writer);
